DclfAlgorithmImpl
public class DcLoadflowImpl
extends AclfNetworkRefImpl
implements DcLoadflow

An implementation of the model object 'Dc Loadflow'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Dclf Calculated
  • Apply Adjustment
  • Adj Max Iterations
  • Adj Tolerance
  • Acc Factor
